overview:
IndoTrading.com is a global e-commerce platform and established to support Small and Medium Enterprises (SMEs) in Indonesia to promote their products online. Indonesia itself now has a large number of SME’s which has the potential to go international market; therefore IndoTrading.com will support them to make it happen. Indotrading.com makes it easy for millions of buyers and suppliers around the world to do business online.

As part of its strategy to transition into a holistic platform where small companies can build and manage their online business more easily, IndoTrading.com also offers a wide array of business management support and consultation, as well as product knowledge and educational services to incubate enterprise management and e-commerce professionals for SME’s.

In this first year of operation, IndoTrading.com has proven the power of e-commerce in generating business opportunities for small businesses and entrepreneurs. Indotrading.com is committed to serving different needs of small businesses and boosting their long-term competitiveness through internet marketing.
